quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,Ma tebbwev ik id tedyant inebgawen ukyisen n Ibôahim
  51,25,"Kecmen $uôes, nnan as: \"tifrat\"! Inna: \"tifrat a wid ur nessin"
  51,26,"Inser ar twacult is, ibbwi d aâjmi iqebbwan"
  51,27,"Iqeôb asen t id; inna: \"day ur teppeppem ara"
  51,28,"Iêus iugad iten. Nnan as: \"ur ppagwad\"! D$a beccôen t s uqcic amusnaw"
  51,29,"Tqeôb ed tmeîîut is, tsu$, tewwet deg udem is, tenna d: \"tam$aôt tiâiqeôt"
  51,30,"Nnan: \"akka id Inna Mass im. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n ûûwab, d Amusnaw"
  51,31,"Inna: \"anwa ay d awal nnwen, a yimceggâan"
  51,32,"Nnan: \"nekwni neppuceggaâ d ar ugdud ibe$wviyen"
  51,33,Iwakken a ten neôoem s uéôu n talaxt
  51,34,i ipwaôecmen s$uô Mass ik i ucmiten
  51,35,"Nessuffe$ kra illan, degs, n lmumnin"
  51,36,"Nufa kan degs, yiwen uxxam n imvuâen"
  51,37,Neooa p id d assekni i wid iugaden aâaqeb aqeôêan
  51,38,"I di Musa, mi t id Nuzen i Ferâun, s udabu n ûûeê"
  51,39,"Iaâûa, akked imalalen is, inna: \"d aseêêar, ne$ d aôehbani"
  51,40,"Neddem it, neppa akked iâsekriwen is, Nveggeô iten ar yill. Tiyta degs"
  51,41,"I di Âad, mi sen Nuzen avu asexvi"
  51,42,"Ur ippaooa ayen immuger, alamma irra t am rrmim"
  51,43,"I Tamud, mi pwanecden: \"siwa tallit ara tezhum"
  51,44,"Âuûan lameô n Mass nnsen. Tewwet iten id ssiâqa, nitni la pwalin"
  51,45,"Ur zmiren a d kren, ur pwasellken"
  51,46,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel, llan, s tidep, d agdud iballa$en"